{% block bodyContent %}

  <p>These page templates combine boilerplate markup and <a href="/design-system/components">components</a> needed for a content page and a transactional page. This includes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>JavaScript that adds a <code>.js-enabled</code> class, which is required by components with JavaScript behaviour</li>
    <li>the <a href="/design-system/components/skip-link">skip link</a>, <a href="/design-system/components/header">header</a> and <a href="/design-system/components/footer">footer</a> components</li>
    <li>favicons, and other page metadata</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Default</h2>

  <p>This example shows the minimum required for a NHS.UK page.</p>

  {{ designExample({
    type: "page-template-default",
    blankpage: true
  }) }}

  <h2>Customised page template</h2>

  <p>You can customise the page template, for example, by adding a service name and navigation or adding a block before the main container to include a <a href="/design-system/components/back-link">back link</a> or <a href="/design-system/components/breadcrumbs">breadcrumbs</a> component.</p>

  <h3>Transactional page template</h3>

  <p>The transactional page template example uses the <a href="/design-system/components/header#transactional-header">transactional header</a> and a <a href="/design-system/components/back-link">back link</a>.</p>

  {{ designExample({
    type: "page-template-transactional",
    blankpage: true
  }) }}

  <p>Vertical padding is reduced on transactional services using the <code>.nhsuk-main-wrapper--s</code> modifier class. It is also recommended to use smaller heading sizes, using the <a href="/design-system/styles/typography#headings">typography headings</a> classes.</p>

  <h3>Content page template</h3>

  <p>The content page template example includes a main navigation and search in the <a href="/design-system/components/header">header</a> and a <a href="/design-system/components/back-link">breadcrumbs</a> component.</p>

  {{ designExample({
    type: "page-template-content",
    blankpage: true
  }) }}

